I really enjoyed doing this course. My only upset was that someone stole my assignment after reviewing, it and posted it as theirs.

Taking this course has helped me get a closer look into academic English at the pre-collegiate level. I especially like how it's timed and engaging students with other learners too making the learning process more realistic and interactive. The written and spoken response approach provided is an interesting way to improve the learner's communication skills. I'm glad to have been able to finish this course in such a limited time and easy access.Thank You Coursera and Rice University !
